sources.description:
A group of small-time crooks devise an elaborate heist, only to see their plan spiral into chaos as egos clash and trust crumbles. Pursued by rival criminals, and the law, their survival hinges on loyalty and cunning in a gritty battle for control.

Original title: Criminal Minds (1998)  Alternative title: Bottom Feeders

Director & Writer: Thomas Baumann
Stars: John Saxon, Dino Tripodis, Kip Ellwood
Genres: Action, Crime, Thriller

Does this film make the cut?  Does it deserve a place in ⭐ B-Movie Hall of Fame ??
